\section{Interests}
\cvitem{Remote sensing for agricultural monitoring}{Study on the effect of climate variability/change and its link to vegetation response by using remote sensing data.}
\cvitem{Data analysis and visualization}{Use of several tools and techniques for spatial and non-spatial data analysis such as exploratory data analysis, cleaning data, regression, inferences, clustering, spatial interpolation and machine-learning/deep-learning.}
\cvitem{Remote Sensing and GIS}{Proven ability to work with large satellite time-series dataset, specially MODIS product from land-team, precipitation satellite products as TRMM, PERSIANN, and CHIRPS.}

